OL,3,CMan jailed for deliberately driving
OL,4,Chead-on into a police car
OL,6,FDash-cam footage has captured the
OL,7,Fmoment a man deliberately drove head-
OL,8,Fon into a police car responding to a
OL,9,F999 call.
OL,11,FThe crash happened on Saturday 7 June
OL,12,F2025 on Crewe Road in Haslington,
OL,13,FCheshire.
OL,15,FOfficers were on their way check on
OL,16,FJoseph Sharpes after receiving a call
OL,17,Fraising concerns for his safety.
OL,19,FThe 22 year left the house before
OL,20,Fpolice could get there and drove in
OL,21,Fthe direction of the officers.
