OL,6,FAs the police car drew close, Sharpes
OL,7,Fdeliberately turned into the officers
OL,8,Fpath hitting them head-on at a
OL,9,Fcombined impact speed estimated to be
OL,10,F80 miles per hour.
OL,12,FTwo police officers and Sharpes were
OL,13,Fhospitalised following the collision
OL,14,Fwith serious injuries.
OL,16,FSharpes was arrested at the scene and
OL,17,Fremained under arrest in hospital
OL,18,Funtil he was released and then
OL,19,Finterviewed, charged and remanded into
OL,20,Fprison.
