OL,3,CMan jailed for deliberately driving
OL,4,Chead-on into a police car
OL,6,FThe 22-year-old from Middlewich
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to causing grievous
OL,8,Fbodily harm with intent, causing
OL,9,Fserious injury by dangerous driving,
OL,10,Factual bodily harm, drug driving and
OL,11,Fpossession of cocaine
OL,13,FOn Monday 17 November Sharpes was
OL,14,Fsentenced at Chester Crown Court to
OL,15,Ffour and a half years in prison.
OL,17,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,18,FSergeant Ryan Ogden, said: "I welcome
OL,19,Fthe custodial sentence handed to
OL,20,FSharpes.
