OL,6,F"The actions of Sharpes not only put
OL,7,Fhimself in danger but also two police
OL,8,Fofficers and other members of the
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,F"Both officers suffered significant
OL,12,Fphysical and psychological injuries as
OL,13,Fa result of the collision. One of them
OL,14,Fhas still not returned to work.
OL,16,F"I also hope the conviction and
OL,17,Frelease of the dash camera footage
OL,18,Fwill help address some of the
OL,19,Finsensitive comments made on social
OL,20,Fmedia at the time apportioning blame
OL,21,Fto the police for the collision."
